{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding prediction intervals, reliability and sharpness are critical performance measures.",
    "PICP is the most widely applied reliability metric, N is the number of samples in the dataset.",
    "y i and ŷi are the actual and predicted wind power generation of the i th sample in the dataset.",
    "y max is the maximum possible wind power output (rated wind power for a wind turbine or installation capacity for a wind farm or a region).",
    "and are hyperparameters which depend on PINC."
  ]
}